The error is due to the addition of a String and Number in Tundra language 
which is not allowed in this context. We need to convert item.price from St
String to Number before adding it with item.fee. Below is the corrected pro
program:

```tundra
def normalize(raw) {
  return {
    price: parseNumber(raw.price),
    fee: parseNumber(raw.fee)
   };
}

val raw = {
  price: "18",
  fee: "2"
};

val item = normalize(raw);
val total = item.price + item.fee;

print(total);
```
This will convert the String values to Number before performing addition an
and then print the result.
